headline.print_headline: Texans Take DE Clowney With First Pick in NFL Draft
headline.main: Texans Take DE Clowney With First Pick in NFL Draft

lead_paragraph: The Houston Texans beefed up their defensive line by taking extraordinary pass rusher Jadeveon Clowney from the University of South Carolina with the first pick of the 2014 National Football League Draft on Thursday.
